<h2>Plans</h2>
<p>
    On the hardware side, I am planning to populate the last drive slots and configure them as a ZFS pool. I
    am also planning on adding an Nvidia P50 or P100 to split across VMs. On the software side, I am planning
    on splitting my docker host into multiple RancherOS instances for configuration with docker swarm or
    kubernetes, using GitLab to host my own repositories, as well as configure my own CI/CD pipeline.
</p>